{
  "stem": "6130.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when I left, she went there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a-- an iron stood there, and that fell on her too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was crushed to death and burned.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was a very big-- and the night was light from the fire bombs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, we didn't care.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We wanted the Americans to come.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We prayed for them to come.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If we die, we die, but they have to come.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So that's how I survived that night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were taken away again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But meanwhile, I stole 60 potatoes-- raw-- and three loaves of bread.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I had an access-- I had through the kitchen, or warehouse, or whatever you want to call it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I knew what's coming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went back and forth, and back and forth, and hid all these things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my niece, and my sister, and I, we-- when we went again, we had 60 potatoes and three loaves of bread.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I never felt richer, and never will feel richer in my life than I felt at that time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because a lot of them on the road just fell aside, dying from hunger and weakness.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we were very smart, and we just had a slice of bread a day and a raw potato or two.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it kept us alive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then, we had to stop again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were told that we had to put into different groups.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had to walk again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they warned us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Those who cannot-- who won't keep up, will be shot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Well, but by that time, we knew that my sister will be never able to keep up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We didn't know how, where to go, how long this will take.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we decided to hide.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We still had potatoes.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
